itemdescription_propertiesprofilename: The name of the profile which holds the origin group.
itemdescription_propertiestrafficrestora: Time in minutes to shift the traffic to the endpoint gradually when an unhealthy endpoint comes healthy or a new endpoint is added. Default is 10 mins. This property is currently not supported.
itemdisplayname_propertiestrafficrestora: Traffic restoration time to healed or new endpoints in minutes
itemdescription_propertiessessionaffinit: Whether to enable use of this rule. Permitted values are 'Enabled' or 'Disabled'
groupdescription_propertiesloadbalancing: Round-Robin load balancing settings for a backend pool
itemdescription_propertiesloadbalancings: The number of samples to consider for load balancing decisions
The number of samples within the sample period that must succeed
The additional latency in milliseconds for probes to fall into the lowest latency bucket
groupdescription_propertieshealthprobese: The JSON object that contains the properties to send health probes to origin.

Protocol to use for health probe.
